{"tid":844694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵客量未符預期　馬時亨：初期數字不作準","createTime":"2018-10-02T05:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T09:11:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"32a2803186e37bd983632ac191e21ce104b10da7","tid":844694,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181002/s00001/ff1a0d5ade6faa8ea360ec67d762c55b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181002%2Fs00001%2Fff1a0d5ade6faa8ea360ec67d762c55b.jpg&h=6035eb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n耗資逾844億元的廣深港高鐵香港段已通車9天，惟當中有公布數字的7天，客量均未達政府下調了的日均8萬人次預測。不過港鐵主席馬時亨稱，日後客量增加時，有人會抱怨西九龍站太細。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段通車以來，日均客量未達政府預期，最少一天更只有預測的四成七。至昨日十一黃金周首日，78,217人次經高鐵西九龍站出入境，是通車以來最高，惟仍未達到政府預測客量。<br />\n<br />\n不過，馬時亨表示，昨日數字已非常接近政府預測，他反而擔心日後客量增加，有人會抱怨西九龍站太小，「大家不要用初期數字去判斷人流，開始時有些人未知道高鐵的方便，我都同一些朋友搭過，他們搭完之後都說以後會搭，加上旅行團現在才剛開始，（港鐵）會做推廣項目&hellip;&hellip;7年後10年後，就有人說這個站太小，15條軌道不夠的了」。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今早出席行政會議前稱，日均8萬人次並非目標，而是「最佳估算」，亦期望可超越這數字。她表示，客量須視乎不同因素，包括班次等，且「一地兩檢」是新事物，市民及旅客需要時間適應。她又說，當以後西九文化區啟用，可吸引更多旅客，故不擔心高鐵香港段財政狀況。"},{"pid":"3d9df883c075432428e1be70c511c04c35392c97","tid":844694,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00001/1538455116857\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00001%2F1538455116857&d=XVj5jUj6%2FfVLMFfG0wJq7Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c79ceb00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181002%2Fs00001%2F1538455116857&h=c2439727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181002/s00001/1538455116857</a>"},{"pid":"a10c8c34547e2f2866e2ce82c27e5ac3c1b9b9d3","tid":844694,"uid":26329,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"無錯 佢話作準先作準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5640e310fb7cb2f2771f3995415f45e03cf30a1c","tid":844694,"uid":57554,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"初期唔計<br />\n放假唔計<br />\n閒日唔計<br />\n所有都唔計"},{"pid":"e193cb8a1795e4dc0debcc818ee579245958f4f3","tid":844694,"uid":153136,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"其實而加人數比預期少咁多，睇新聞都已經有人屌緊唔夠大，睇嚟係專登起細d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd5068c3eb988ed11ebbc609b3257e314176766","tid":844694,"uid":6869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1d21a1c28302dd03c692342b7e9d06a4a251494","tid":844694,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"中期數字不作準"},{"pid":"f081b11daf572f9c42d39f1d8898ff0c67cac3ee","tid":844694,"uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"達哥：今次唔算"},{"pid":"6f79d840868b8f994b1d38d7d98bf7d8e73ae42a","tid":844694,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"數據唔達標<br />\n唔計"},{"pid":"64983189028ecd3992a9d7f1b411c6995215d746","tid":844694,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T05:56:17.000Z","msg":"千祈咪公開政府補貼數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb8dc057d1a66457aa91367a3a9fd9cc9759106","tid":844694,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"未來二十年都係初期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9668d730fdb6d6af9e4a2e05869e008b62832f65","tid":844694,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim